{"tid":2304097,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4/12 如果請假無返學，會否犯國安法？","createTime":"2020-11-28T13:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T22:46:15.000Z","uid":2719,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8fad6dfccdec642fc637bcce58615837fb14fc75","tid":2304097,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:08:06.000Z","msg":"如果請病假就問你拎醫生紙證明，證明唔到就家長教唆分裂國家之類。<br />\n<br />\n而請事假，九萬幾個理由任講其實都得，主要係想知嗰日無返，會點？<br />\n<br />\n如果無乜野只係記下缺點呢啲垃圾懲罰，就年年都請吹你唔脹。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗講咩根本就唔應該我地避，4/12就唔應該有呢啲廢話，你唔會阻止到。<br />\n<br />\n同埋，我真係想香港人係嗰一日就俾仔女唔返學，睇下全港咁多學生同一日無返學，會有咩迴響，同時睇下班港共為咗奶共，會有咩戇鳩跟進方案都好。"},{"pid":"1ca89e7edbebcbe5de9986e441813f9679f8ddce","tid":2304097,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:14:16.000Z","msg":"實mark低邊個請假<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b56aef3e507cdddb5b82706bc98dd280c16e3a3","tid":2304097,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:41:56.000Z","msg":"上呼吸道感染4大病徵<br />\n發燒 咳 喉嚨痛 流鼻水<br />\n是但中兩樣 冇人敢俾人返學"},{"pid":"a2c3f1796f04921c8bb70de05de259fec1fa2453","tid":2304097,"uid":288304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:43:07.000Z","msg":"果日除非死左，如果唔係同學連家長都要寫悔過書"},{"pid":"0c156a9211405a5a88aa0df5cb25673b66b9644d","tid":2304097,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:44:29.000Z","msg":"一係隔離一係送中"},{"pid":"14a481b7f9909b306b4152a7d42ab108bc7f838f","tid":2304097,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:48:10.000Z","msg":"係咪真係咁乖個個都返 好似無乜人諗過咁返咁"},{"pid":"15d6b875efacba5c09a9af32a431b3f9e02db4ad","tid":2304097,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T19:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />身體入面每粒細胞都感謝中央"},{"pid":"9b4ff37fcb71150c1cdd811dd3ff8ee75eafa1e4","tid":2304097,"uid":105691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited